headline: Title Resources Group Adds Accomplished Title Professional to Expand East Coast and Midwest Territories
summary: Title Resources Group (TRG), one of the nation's leading title insurance underwriters, has appointed Janell Downing as Agency Account Manager for Ohio, New Jersey and Pennsylvania. A seasoned title professional, Downing will drive business development efforts in these territories by forming and managing relationships with title insurance agents while supporting their growth initiatives.
